{"tid":1874062,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有康美樓居民被送往美孚「翠雅山房」隔離　有黨衛軍駐守","createTime":"2020-02-11T03:51:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T03:51:35.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"807427a79dfa467afcfbf840423e3c80584495de","tid":1874062,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:51:35.000Z","msg":"有康美樓居民被送往「翠雅山房」隔離 有警員駐守<br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒疫情持續，青衣長康邨康美樓07單位的住客，因為同號單位有兩名住戶確診染病而要撤離，以進行檢疫，部分人士被送到美孚饒宗頤文化館的「翠雅山房」。「翠雅山房」今早未見有人進出，門外有警員駐守，亦禁止傳媒內進。<br />\n<br />\n「翠雅山房」大閘緊閉，在內駐守的警員拒絕傳媒入內採訪，閘內共6名戴上外科口罩的警員看守，大閘外的兩段行人路亦拉起封鎖線。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507865-20200211.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507865-20200211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=29a7f891\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507865-20200211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f7afa69a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507865-20200211.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}